videos.description: Jonas Valanciunas passes to Ja Morant under the basket for a layup.

videos.headline: Valanciunas drops it off to Morant for the layup

videos.description: Ja Morant slings a nice pass to Dillon Brooks, who knocks down a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Morant's slick pass finds Brooks for 3-pointer) 2021/02/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Morant's slick pass finds Brooks for 3-pointer

videos.description: Anthony Davis blocks Xavier Tillman's layup attempt and then Kentavious Caldwell-Pope hits a 3-pointer at the other end.

videos.headline: AD's block leads to KCP's 3-pointer

videos.description: With time running out in the first half, Ja Morant throws up an off-balanced 3-pointer and gets it to fall as the buzzer sounds.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Morant beats the buzzer with 3-pointer) 2021/02/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Morant beats the buzzer with 3-pointer

videos.description: LeBron James goes on a mini tear at the end of the third, hitting three straight shots to push the Lakers out front of the Grizzlies.

videos.headline: LeBron hits 3 straight shots to help give Lakers first lead

videos.description: Marc Gasol passes to a driving LeBron James, who rocks the rim with a one-handed jam.

videos.headline: LeBron goes baseline for tomahawk dunk

videos.description: After being down 20 early on, LeBron James leads the Lakers to a comeback win vs. the Grizzlies with 28 points, nine rebounds and eight assists.
